item.title: I will Sing of the Mercies of the Lord
item.description: I will sing of the mercies of the Lord Forever I will sing, I will sing. I will sing of the mercies of the Lord, Forever I will sing of the mercies of the Lord. With my mouth will I make known, Thy faithfulness, Thy faithfulness. With my mouth will I make known, Thy faithfulness to all generations.
